snippet.title: Patrick Tugwell
snippet.description:
Christian Singer-Songwriter, Patrick Tugwell has been songwriting for the church for a number of years. Because of his leadership in his local church community, and ability to compose worship music for congregations and bands alike, his music has become a mantra for the surrounding Herndon Virginia community. Looking to continue to lead others to Christ, we are prayerful that his music will continue to touch more and more lives globally.

In addition, Patrick's business life has been one of much success. He is one of the most sought-after trainers in Network Marketing today. In the past few years Patrick has quickly become one of Neora's top leaders, a multi-billion dollar international company. Having been a leader in the industry, Patrick has built organizations in many countries around the world. 

Hablo español!

International Contact: +1 (703) 927-1771
Email: pmtugwel@gmail.com

Facebook.com/patrick.tugwell
Instagram.com/patricktugwell
